動。部分區域限制只准旅客、工作人員、機場保安進入。"},{"pid":"bbc1f8e74b470a84d378353d34bdf82ad7a55b95","tid":1468534,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:07:06.000Z","msg":"禁制令阻止任何人，故意妨礙在機場區內或附近任何道路，通道，入口或出口或出入口等。<br />\n<br />\n《立場》晚上曾向機管局查詢禁制令內容、是否獲法庭批出禁制令，暫時未獲回覆。"},{"pid":"a0794c1c48b1230a76023e62ee92bc78bfadc059","tid":1468534,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:07:43.000Z","msg":"法庭要求，機管局在機場的顯眼地方安全地傳送傳訊令，命令及傳票的副本；在網站 <a href=\"http://www.hongkongairport.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongairport.com&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHU6joMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=d602b397\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.hongkongairport.com</a>上張貼傳訊令，命令及傳票，以及連續3天在香港的一份英文報章及一份中文報章刊登傳訊令，命令及傳票的副本。"},{"pid":"3a98b489f93e8cf37fcfc0b40974f7d72ec936cf","tid":1468534,"uid":295455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80c5def57b39610a70ddbaf099a68df2cbf64610","tid":1468534,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:06:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E5%8D%97%E6%97%A9-%E6%A9%9F%E7%AE%A1%E5%B1%80%E7%8D%B2%E6%B3%95%E5%BA%AD%E7%A6%81%E5%88%B6%E4%BB%A4-%E7%A6%81%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E5%A6%A8%E7%A4%99%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E9%81%8B%E4%BD%9C/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%258D%2597%25E6%2597%25A9-%25E6%25A9%259F%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E5%25B1%2580%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E7%25A6%2581%25E5%2588%25B6%25E4%25BB%25A4-%25E7%25A6%2581%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%25A6%25A8%25E7%25A4%2599%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E9%2581%258B%25E4%25BD%259C%2F&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHU6joMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=68fa5097\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%258D%2597%25E6%2597%25A9-%25E6%25A9%259F%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E5%25B1%2580%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BA%25AD%25